;a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:426:\"<p>Looking for the best blogging tools to help boost your online business? Choosing the right blogging tools can help you rank your blog high on search engine results pages (SERPs), leading to more traffic. Some can also help you discover&#8230;</p>\nThe post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-blogging-tools/\">12 Blogging Tools to Help You Grow Your WordPress Blog</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Kato Nkhoma\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35287:\"<p>Looking for the best blogging tools to help boost your online business?</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Choosing the right blogging tools can help you rank your blog high on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-are-serps/\" title=\"What Are SERPs (And Why Are they Important to SEO)?\">search engine results pages</a> (SERPs), leading to more traffic. Some can also help you discover growth opportunities, resulting in you reaching a wider audience and an increase in your earning potential.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In this article, we will show you some of the best blogging tools you can use to grow your WordPress blog and increase your revenue.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"is-layout-flow wp-block-group aioseo-table-of-contents has-theme-info-background-color has-background\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In This Article</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-aioseo-table-of-contents\"><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-11-blogging-tools-to-grow-your-wordpress-blog-our-expert-picks\">12 Blogging Tools to Grow Your WordPress Blog: Our Expert Picks</a><ul><li><a href=\"#aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. All In One SEO (AIOSEO)</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-2-seedprod\">2. SeedProd</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-3-optinmonster\">3. OptinMonster</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-4-wpforms\">4. WPForms</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-5-sendlayer\">5. SendLayer</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-6-monsterinsights\">6. MonsterInsights</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-7-pushengage\">7. PushEngage</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-8-rafflepress\">8. RafflePress</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-9-smash-balloon\">9. Smash Balloon</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-10-ahrefs\">10. Ahrefs</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-10-semrush\">11. Semrush</a></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-11-better-click-to-tweet\">12. Better Click to Tweet</a></li></ul></li><li><a href=\"#aioseo-the-best-blogging-tools-to-help-you-grow-your-wordpress-blog-our-top-picks\">The Best Blogging Tools to Help You Grow Your WordPress Blog: Our Top Picks</a></li></ul></div>\n</div></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-11-blogging-tools-to-grow-your-wordpress-blog-our-expert-picks\">12 Blogging Tools to Grow Your WordPress Blog: Our Expert Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>With so many blogging tools on the market, choosing the right ones for your business can be daunting. So, we’ve taken out the hard work and curated this expertly picked list of the top blogging tools to consider when turning your WordPress website into an online store.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-1-all-in-one-seo-aioseo\">1. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">All In One SEO</a> (AIOSEO)</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"311\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png\" alt=\"aioseo homepage\" class=\"wp-image-151544\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-300x133.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/aioseo-600x267.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a> is a powerful yet easy-to-use SEO plugin that has been downloaded over 100 million times. Millions of smart bloggers use AIOSEO to help them boost their search engine rankings and drive qualified traffic to their eCommerce sites. That’s because the plugin has many powerful features and modules designed to help you properly configure your SEO settings. Examples include:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Search Statistics:</strong> This powerful <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/google-search-console-integration/\" title=\"Announcing AIOSEO 4.3.0 – Get Powerful Insights With Our Google Search Console Integration\">Google Search Console integration</a> lets you track your keyword rankings and see important SEO metrics with 1-click, and more.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Redirection Manager</strong>: Helps you <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/redirection-manager/\" title=\"Redirection Manager\">manage redirects</a> and eliminate 404 errors, making it easier for search engines to crawl and index your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Link Assistant</strong>: Powerful internal linking tool that <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/ways-link-assistant-can-save-you-time-on-internal-and-external-link-building/\" title=\"6 Ways Link Assistant Can Save You Time On Internal Link Building\">automates building links</a> between pages on your site. It also gives you an audit of outbound links.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>SEO Preview</strong>: This gives you an <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-the-seo-preview-tool/\" title=\"What is the SEO Preview Tool (And How to Use it to Drive More Traffic)?\">overview of your search and social snippets</a> and general SEO so you can improve your optimization.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>IndexNow:</strong> For fast indexing on search engines that support the <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/what-is-indexnow-for-seo/\" title=\"What is IndexNow for SEO (Explained in Plain English)?\">IndexNow protocol</a> (like Bing and Yandex).</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Sitemap generator</strong>: Automatically generate <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-a-sitemap-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Sitemap in WordPress (The Easy Way)\">different types of sitemaps</a> to notify all search engines of any updates on your site.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/features/\">And more</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>AIOSEO also has other powerful tools for bloggers to help your blog posts rank and drive traffic. One such tool is TrueSEO. This is a powerful content optimization tool that helps you create SEO-friendly content. It helps you ​​easily add title tags, meta descriptions, keywords, and everything else you need for proper on-page SEO optimization.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, the Page Analysis feature is pretty handy as it gives insight into how well you’ve optimized your post. It also gives you recommendations for improving your content.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"288\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-aioseo-page-analysis.png\" alt=\"The Page Analysis in AIOSE is a fantastic tool that helps you optimize your posts.\" class=\"wp-image-163386\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-aioseo-page-analysis.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-aioseo-page-analysis-300x123.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-aioseo-page-analysis-600x246.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-aioseo-page-analysis-146x60.png 146w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-aioseo-page-analysis-219x90.png 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Another SEO feature many bloggers love in AIOSEO is <strong>Link Assistant</strong>. This is an AI-powered internal link building tool that helps you automatically build links between relevant pages on your blog.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"700\" height=\"381\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/link-assistant-2.png\" alt=\"The Links Report dashboard gives you insight into linking opportunities and orphaned pages.\" class=\"wp-image-70919\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/link-assistant-2.png 700w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/link-assistant-2-300x163.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/link-assistant-2-600x327.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Internal link building is a fantastic on-page SEO that can help your articles rank and increase visitors&#8217; time on your site.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The SEO modules in AIOSEO are super easy to use, even if you don’t have any technical or coding knowledge. This makes AIOSEO the best blogging tool for beginner bloggers and experts alike.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Last but certainly not least comes the built-in <strong>Headline Analyzer</strong>. This powerful tool can help you optimize your blog post headlines for search and higher clickthrough rates (CTR).</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can use the <strong>Headline Analyzer</strong> in the post editor.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"704\" height=\"528\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/blogging-tools-headline-analyzer.png\" alt=\"The Haedline Analyser is the best blogging tool for optimizing blog posts.\" class=\"wp-image-163388\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/blogging-tools-headline-analyzer.png 704w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/blogging-tools-headline-analyzer-300x225.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/blogging-tools-headline-analyzer-600x450.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/blogging-tools-headline-analyzer-80x60.png 80w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/blogging-tools-headline-analyzer-120x90.png 120w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Or you can use the standalone Headline Analyzer under the SEO Analysis tab in AIOSEO…&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"339\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/optimize-blog-titles-headline-analyzer-score.png\" alt=\"You get a score out of 100 for your headline.\" class=\"wp-image-163389\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/optimize-blog-titles-headline-analyzer-score.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/optimize-blog-titles-headline-analyzer-score-300x145.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/optimize-blog-titles-headline-analyzer-score-600x290.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/optimize-blog-titles-headline-analyzer-score-124x60.png 124w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/optimize-blog-titles-headline-analyzer-score-186x90.png 186w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re a blogger, AIOSEO is the best <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-seo-plugins-for-wordpress/\" title=\"8 Best SEO Plugins for WordPress in 2023 (Tried and Tested)\">WordPress SEO plugin</a> to grow your audience and business.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>For step-by-step instructions on how to install AIOSEO, check our <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/docs/installing-all-in-one-seo-pro/\" title=\"Installing All in One SEO Pro\">detailed installation guide</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>While the free version of AIOSEO can help you boost your rankings and drive traffic to your blog, the premium versions give you a greater competitive edge.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Starts at $49.60.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-2-seedprod\">2. <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"SeedProd\">SeedProd</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"706\" height=\"400\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod.png\" alt=\"SeedProd is one of the best blogging tools for building websites or landing pages.\" class=\"wp-image-99505\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod.png 706w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod-300x170.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/best-free-wordpress-plugins-seedprod-600x340.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 706px) 100vw, 706px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"SeedProd\">SeedProd</a> is undoubtedly the best website and page builder plugin for WordPress. Unsurprisingly, over 1 million professionals use it to build their websites. It’s a lightweight page builder designed with speed and SEO in mind.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Users love SeedProd because of its powerful drag-and-drop page builder that makes it easy to use. The plugin also has beautiful templates and pre-designed sections like headers and calls to action. All these make building your blog easy, even if you don’t have any technical or coding skills.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>SeedProd is also popular for its versatility. You can use it to create any type of website, including portfolio sites, business websites, non-profit websites, and more. And adding a blog to these is super easy. And with so many customization options, you can create a unique blog that stands out. For those times when you’re working on your site, SeedProd allows you to put your webs