ttps://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-diy-seo-software-tools-ahrefs-183x90.png 183w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a> is a comprehensive marketing and SEO toolkit to help you DIY your SEO as a blogger. It also has powerful keyword research and competitor analysis tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can use Ahrefs for keyword discovery, uncovering backlink opportunities, rank tracking, and more. You can use this data to develop impactful SEO strategies to help you outperform your competitors.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Another noteworthy feature you’ll love in Ahrefs is the Content Explorer. This tool shows you the most popular content ranking for a particular keyword. You can use it to reverse engineer the SEO strategy behind the winning articles.&nbsp;<strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $99.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-10-semrush\">11. <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush\">Semrush</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"425\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush.png\" alt=\"Semrush is the best all-in-one marketing tool.\" class=\"wp-image-163413\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush-300x182.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush-600x363.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush-99x60.png 99w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-semrush-149x90.png 149w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush\">Semrush</a> is an all-in-one SEO and content marketing tool that helps you find competitive search data so your blog can rank high for the right keywords. It also gives you insights into your competitors’ strategies in display advertising, organic and paid search, and link building.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Semrush really shines when it comes to keyword research. One reason for this is that besides showing you search volumes and keyword difficulty, it also shows you the search intent behind your keywords. This helps ensure you use the right keywords and create content your readers will find helpful. And when writing your blog posts, you can use <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/semrush-seo-writing-assistant/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Semrush Writing Assistant\">Semrush’s Writing Assistant</a> to help optimize your content.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Paid plans start at $119.95. A free plan is available, but it’s very limited.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Best Semrush alternatives: <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/ahrefs/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Ahrefs\">Ahrefs</a> and <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/recommends/mangools/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"Mangools\">Mangools</a> suite of SEO tools.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"aioseo-11-better-click-to-tweet\">12. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/better-click-to-tweet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Better Click to Tweet\">Better Click to Tweet</a></h3>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/better-click-to-tweet/\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"702\" height=\"310\" src=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-better-click-to-tweet.png\" alt=\"Better Click to Tweet lets you add &quot;click to tweet&quot; buttons in your blog posts.\" class=\"wp-image-163414\" srcset=\"https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-better-click-to-tweet.png 702w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-better-click-to-tweet-300x132.png 300w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-better-click-to-tweet-600x265.png 600w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-better-click-to-tweet-136x60.png 136w, https://aioseo.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/best-blogging-tools-better-click-to-tweet-204x90.png 204w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 702px) 100vw, 702px\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/better-click-to-tweet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"Better Click to Tweet\">Better Click to Tweet</a> is a free WordPress plugin that lets you insert ‘click to tweet’ buttons into your blog posts or other pages on your site. It makes it easy for your readers to quickly and easily tweet a quote from your content. This helps turn your readers into brand ambassadors, thereby increasing your reach.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The plugin has a special Gutenberg block, making it easy to use. Alternatively, you can use a shortcode to insert the ‘click to tweet’ button into your posts.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Pricing</strong>: Free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"aioseo-the-best-blogging-tools-to-help-you-grow-your-wordpress-blog-our-top-picks\">The Best Blogging Tools to Help You Grow Your WordPress Blog: Our Top Picks</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Our top pick for the best blogging tool to help you grow your WordPress blog is <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/pricing/\" title=\"Pricing\">AIOSEO</a>. It’s a powerful plugin that can help you improve your visibility on search engines. It also helps boost clickthrough rates and ensure your content is optimized for search engines and users.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want a plugin to help you build a fast-loading website, then <a href=\"https://www.seedprod.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" title=\"SeedProd\">SeedProd</a> is it.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope this post helped you find the best WordPress eCommerce plugin for your business. You may also want to check out other articles on our blog, like <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-start-a-small-business-blog/\" title=\"How to Start a Small Business Blog in 2023\">how to start a small business blog</a> or our tutorial on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/how-to-create-jump-links-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create Jump Links in WordPress (and Increase Your Visibility On SERPs)\">creating jump links in WordPress</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you found this article helpful, then please subscribe to our <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/AIOSEO\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">YouTube Channel</a>. You’ll find many more helpful tutorials there. You can also follow us on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aioseopack\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Twitter</a>, <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/aioseo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">LinkedIn</a>, or <a href=\"https://facebook.com/aioseopack/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" title=\"\">Facebook</a> to stay in the loop. </p>The post <a href=\"https://aioseo.com/best-blogging-tools/\">12 Blogging Tools to Help You Grow Your WordPress Blog</a> first appeared on <a href=\"https://aioseo.com\">AIOSEO</a>.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:44:\"https://aioseo.com/best-blogging-tools/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:97:\"\n		\n		\n		